<Window x:Class="WpfApp.Pupils_Free"
        xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
        xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
        xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008"
        xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006"
        xmlns:local="clr-namespace:WpfApp"
        xmlns:components="clr-namespace:WpfApp.Components"
        mc:Ignorable="d"
        Title="Pupils_Free" Height="604" Width="537">
    <Grid Background="LightBlue" Margin="0,0,0,-6">
        <!-- StackPanel for layout -->
        <StackPanel HorizontalAlignment="Center" VerticalAlignment="Center">
            <!-- TextBlock for Title -->
            <TextBlock Text="Pupils Facilities Free" 
                   FontSize="24" 
                   FontWeight="Bold" 
                   Foreground="DarkBlue" 
                   HorizontalAlignment="Center" 
                   Margin="0,10,0,20"/>

            <!-- Placeholder for descriptive text -->
            <ScrollViewer VerticalScrollBarVisibility="Auto" HorizontalScrollBarVisibility="Disabled" Height="180" Width="423">
                <TextBox TextWrapping="Wrap" IsReadOnly="True" Background="White" BorderBrush="Transparent" 
         FontSize="16" FontFamily="Georgia" Padding="10" TextAlignment="Center">
                    <TextBox.Text>
                        <![CDATA[

At MTC, we are proud to offer free transportation facilities for school pupils, ensuring they can travel safely and conveniently without financial burden. Here’s how we support young learners:

1. **Free Bus Passes**  
   - Pupils up to a certain grade level are eligible for free bus passes, which can be used for unlimited rides to and from school.

2. **Dedicated School Routes**  
   - Specially designed routes to cover schools across the city, ensuring timely and safe transport for pupils.

3. **Safety First**  
   - All buses for pupils are equipped with CCTV, GPS tracking, and trained staff to ensure the highest level of safety and security.

4. **Digital Pass Management**  
   - Parents and guardians can manage free passes through our app, allowing real-time tracking and seamless renewal.

5. **Inclusive Facilities**  
   - Our buses are accessible to pupils with special needs, providing ramps, priority seating, and other support.

**How to Avail Free Facilities?**  
- Register your child through our app or at the nearest MTC office.  
- Provide proof of enrollment in a recognized school.  
- Collect the free bus pass and enjoy hassle-free commuting!  

Let’s make education more accessible with free transportation for pupils. Together, we’re building a brighter future!
                        ]]>
                    </TextBox.Text>
                </TextBox>
            </ScrollViewer>

            <!-- Placeholder for an image -->
            <Image Source="{Binding Source={x:Static components:Resource.Pupils_Facilities}}" 
               Width="300" 
               Height="200" 
               HorizontalAlignment="Center" 
               Margin="0,20,0,0"/>
        </StackPanel>
    </Grid>
</Window>
